title: 57: OBITCH who nose!
description:
Get in Geoffs we’re going to the future this week as Spencer takes us through the Digital Afterlife, but first Madison is giving us a lesson on the wild origins of plastic surgery! We’ve got an obituary that’s a little backwards….and one for a true badass! Oh, and of course, we’ve got some dumb.ass.criminallllls! 


New episodes come out every (day of week) for free, with 1-week early access for Wondery+ subscribers.
